      "The buyer pool for East Hill is specific and consistent: professionals, creatives, and families who value character over square footage; buyers relocating from cities who recognize historic urban neighborhoods and know what they're worth; downsizers leaving larger homes who want the richness of an established community. This creates steady, predictable demand.",
      "## East Hill Life: What It's Actually Like to Live Here",
